<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٣٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/941">بِشْرُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3875">عَبْدُ اللهِ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3037">عَاصِمٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1562">حَفْصَةَ بِنْتِ سِيرِينَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«الطَّاعُونُ شَهَادَةٌ لِكُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>